data.description: Lots of Charm and Character in this 3 Br, 2 Bath cottage in desirable Old East Rome. Updated kitchen and baths, large laundry room/ mud room could be additional pantry, or art/project room with the original wrap around windows. Recent updates include new double pane windows, vinyl siding, 7 yr old roof.  Shared drive leads to off street parking and a great  storage building.  One bedroom is currently being used as a study/ den.  Beautiful wood floors and wood beams, columns and moldings are still intact from its original construction in the early 1920’s… Easy to show on short notice! Call or text  Mimi-706-506-9634. and go SELL!
